content:
Managing Your Templates

Existing templates that you or other CRM Analytics admins created are manageable from CRM Analytics Studio. You can update, decouple from source apps, and delete templates. Before they can be deleted, templates must be decoupled from their source app.

To create and manage templates: 
CRM Analytics Growth permission set license with Manage CRM Analytics Template Apps user permission

To update a template:
Click on the three dots on the right of the template
Click Update

To delete a template:
Decouple it from the source app
Click on the three dots on the right of the template
Click Decouple App and confirm
Review again and click Delete
title: Managing CRM Analytics Templates
